<HEAD>Federal Judge Rules State Can Keep Creche in Front Of Capitol</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: LEADS with 8 grafs to CORRECT in 2nd graf that judge's
deadline is Monday sted week's end, and to delete incorrect
